    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 1
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "1. Overview"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The stored procedure "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "aspnet_CheckSchemaVersion",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " is designed to verify the compatibility of a specific feature's schema version within a database. It checks whether a given feature and its associated schema version exist in the "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "aspnet_SchemaVersions",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " table. If the specified feature and version are found, the procedure returns 0, indicating compatibility. If not found, it returns 1, indicating incompatibility or absence."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 1
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "2. Complexity Level: Low"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The procedure is straightforward, involving a simple query to check for the existence of a record in a table. It does not involve complex logic, multiple steps, or intricate data manipulations."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 1
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "3. Input Parameters"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "bulletList",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "@Feature nvarchar(128)",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "code"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ": This parameter represents the name of the feature whose schema version is being checked. It is expected to be a string with a maximum length of 128 characters."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "@CompatibleSchemaVersion nvarchar(128)",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "code"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ": This parameter represents the version of the schema that is considered compatible. It is also a string with a maximum length of 128 characters."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 1
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "4. Business Logic and Workflow"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "orderedList",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "The procedure begins by checking if a record exists in the "
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "aspnet_SchemaVersions",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "code"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " table where:"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "bulletList",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "listItem",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "type": "paragraph",
                      "content": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": "The "
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": "Feature",
                          "marks": [
                            {
                              "type": "code"
                            }
                          ]
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": " column matches the lowercase version of the "
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": "@Feature",
                          "marks": [
                            {
                              "type": "code"
                            }
                          ]
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": " parameter."
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "listItem",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "type": "paragraph",
                      "content": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": "The "
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": "CompatibleSchemaVersion",
                          "marks": [
                            {
                              "type": "code"
                            }
                          ]
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": " column matches the "
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": "@CompatibleSchemaVersion",
                          "marks": [
                            {
                              "type": "code"
                            }
                          ]
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "text": " parameter."
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "If such a record exists, the procedure returns 0, indicating that the feature's schema version is compatible."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "If no matching record is found, the procedure returns 1, indicating that the feature's schema version is not compatible or does not exist in the table."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 1
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "5. Performance Considerations"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "bulletList",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "The performance of this procedure is primarily dependent on the indexing of the "
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "aspnet_SchemaVersions",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "code"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " table. If the "
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Feature",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "code"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " and "
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "CompatibleSchemaVersion",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "code"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " columns are indexed, the query will execute efficiently."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "The use of the "
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "LOWER",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "code"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " function on the "
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "@Feature",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "code"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " parameter ensures case-insensitive comparison, which may affect performance if the column is not indexed with a case-insensitive collation."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "The procedure performs a simple existence check, which is generally fast, but performance could degrade if the table grows significantly without proper indexing."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 1
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "6. Potential Issues or Risks"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "bulletList",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Case Sensitivity",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "strong"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ": The use of the "
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "LOWER",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "code"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " function assumes that the "
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Feature",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "code"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " column is stored in a case-insensitive manner. If the database collation is case-sensitive, this could lead to unexpected results."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Parameter Length",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "strong"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ": The procedure does not validate the length of the input parameters beyond the database's inherent constraints. If the input exceeds 128 characters, it will be truncated, potentially leading to incorrect results."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Schema Changes",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "strong"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ": Any changes to the structure or naming of the "
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "aspnet_SchemaVersions",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "code"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " table could break the procedure if not updated accordingly."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Error Handling",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "strong"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ": The procedure lacks error handling mechanisms. If an error occurs during execution, it will not be caught or logged, which could complicate troubleshooting efforts."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 1
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "7. Stored Procedure Definition"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "codeBlock",
      "attrs": {
        "language": "sql"
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[aspnet_CheckSchemaVersion]\n    @Feature                   nvarchar(128),\r\n    @CompatibleSchemaVersion   nvarchar(128)\r\nAS\r\nBEGIN\r\n    IF (EXISTS( SELECT  *\r\n                FROM dbo.aspnet_SchemaVersions\r\n                WHERE   Feature = LOWER( @Feature ) AND\r\n                        CompatibleSchemaVersion = @CompatibleSchemaVersion ))\r\n        RETURN 0\r\n\r\n    RETURN 1\r\nEND"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
